<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3527534>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Scanning electron micrographs showing the distal part of Progonyleptoidellus spp. penis: A–B, P. bocaina sp. nov. (MZSP 18939), A. dorsal, B. lateral; C–D, P. picinguaba sp. nov. (MZSP 16259), A. dorsal, B. lateral. Scale bars: 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3527534/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

